280
00:20:32,900 --> 00:20:34,810
- Hello.
- Hi.

281
00:20:34,810 --> 00:20:38,280
I work with...

282
00:20:38,280 --> 00:20:40,570
Cayman.

283
00:20:40,570 --> 00:20:42,990
