284
00:20:44,210 --> 00:20:46,840
Fang Xiaoyu.

285
00:20:46,840 --> 00:20:50,980
Fang Xiaoyu. Fang Xiaoyu.

286
00:20:52,300 --> 00:20:54,520
Fang Xiaoyu...

287
00:20:54,520 --> 00:20:56,730
Fang Xiaoyu.

288
00:20:56,730 --> 00:20:59,640
He's my friend.

289
00:20:59,640 --> 00:21:02,560
This lady is here to look for Director Fang.

290
00:21:02,560 --> 00:21:04,570
How about we give him a call?

291
00:21:05,830 --> 00:21:08,220
