292
00:21:08,220 --> 00:21:11,160
She might even be Director Fang's lover.

293
00:21:11,160 --> 00:21:13,300
Let her in.

294
00:21:13,300 --> 00:21:16,040
- Please, we welcome you.
- Welcome.

295
00:21:17,690 --> 00:21:20,850
But she must be allowed in.

296
00:21:39,890 --> 00:21:42,550
I'm here to see someone. I'm with Director Fang.

297
00:21:42,550 --> 00:21:45,100
Does anyone speak Chinese here?

298
00:21:49,930 --> 00:21:52,420
Madam? Yes, you...

299
00:21:52,420 --> 00:21:54,240
Why are you still here?

300
00:21:54,240 --> 00:21:56,070
Hurry, hurry.

301
00:22:01,080 --> 00:22:05,170
Girls, let me have a look at your number card.

302
00:22:05,170 --> 00:22:07,010
Take your numbers.

303
00:22:07,010 --> 00:22:10,680
How's it feeling? Good?

304
00:22:10,680 --> 00:22:13,020
Good.

305
00:22:13,020 --> 00:22:16,560
Everyone you want.

306
00:22:16,560 --> 00:22:18,880
Please get ready fast.

307
00:22:18,880 --> 00:22:23,700
So, guys, you know everything, right? What to do. How to walk. How to smile.

308
00:22:23,700 --> 00:22:28,140
How to get what you want. So I wish you luck. And you are the best.

309
00:22:28,140 --> 00:22:30,680
Thank you.

310
00:23:04,520 --> 00:23:08,710
Director Fang, shall we lower the bar a little? Otherwise, no one will get to stay.

311
00:23:19,920 --> 00:23:21,700
Wait.

312
00:23:21,700 --> 00:23:26,160
I hope that next time you walk to here,

313
00:23:26,160 --> 00:23:28,830
