314
00:23:28,830 --> 00:23:31,830
Your body is really beautiful.

315
00:23:31,830 --> 00:23:34,760
More eyesight...

316
00:23:34,760 --> 00:23:37,740
Yes, yes, very good.

317
00:24:59,930 --> 00:25:02,190
What are you doing here?

318
00:25:03,990 --> 00:25:07,670
I'm a model. Isn't this where I'm supposed to be?

319
00:25:12,930 --> 00:25:17,110
If I remember correctly, Cayman fired you a long time ago.

320
00:25:19,820 --> 00:25:21,980
Do you remember?

321
00:25:22,710 --> 00:25:26,730
I became a model because of you.

322
00:25:31,660 --> 00:25:34,290
The first time I walked on the runway,

323
00:25:35,350 --> 00:25:38,360
you were walking with me, by my side.

324
00:25:38,360 --> 00:25:42,450
- I don't remember.
- But I do. I...

325
00:25:42,450 --> 00:25:45,820
What's going on? Are you just letting anyone walk in here now?

326
00:25:45,820 --> 00:25:48,810
I'm so sorry, Director Fang. This is all on me.

327
00:25:48,810 --> 00:25:51,010
I'll take her out now.

328
00:25:52,300 --> 00:25:54,360
Let's go. You are making a scene here.

329
00:25:56,800 --> 00:25:58,600
You...

330
00:26:00,050 --> 00:26:01,960
I...

331
00:26:01,960 --> 00:26:03,730
Please get up.

332
00:26:03,730 --> 00:26:05,320
I can't.

333
00:26:05,320 --> 00:26:07,600
I strained my ankle and broke my heel.

334
00:26:07,600 --> 00:26:10,650
- Putting on a show again, aren't we?
- No.

335
00:26:12,450 --> 00:26:14,800
Director Fang, the heel is broken.

336
00:26:20,600 --> 00:26:22,650
What do you want?

337
00:26:22,650 --> 00:26:25,190
I have important things to tell you.

338
00:26:25,190 --> 00:26:27,740
What do you have to say to me that's so important?

339
00:26:28,270 --> 00:26:30,620
Drag her out.

340
00:26:30,620 --> 00:26:33,600
It's really important. It's about work.

341
00:26:33,600 --> 00:26:35,670
Do what I say.

342
00:26:35,670 --> 00:26:38,730
Fang Xiaoyu, you are just too much, you know?

343
00:26:39,360 --> 00:26:41,450
Look, you got up.

344
00:26:41,450 --> 00:26:44,310
- I...
- Take her to my office.

345
00:26:46,430 --> 00:26:49,960
Let's go. Can you walk?

346
00:26:59,600 --> 00:27:03,510
Li Qi, go get a pair of shoes for Ms. Bai.

347
00:27:04,500 --> 00:27:08,020
- Shoes?
- Yes. Now.

348
00:27:08,020 --> 00:27:10,140
Okay.

349
00:27:14,870 --> 00:27:18,660
Director Fang, we are in France.

350
00:27:18,660 --> 00:27:21,610
Can you at least have some compassion for your fellow Chinese?

351
00:27:25,970 --> 00:27:30,100
I'm sorry. With you, I really can't.

352
00:27:30,100 --> 00:27:32,870
Can't you be a little bit nicer to me?

353
00:27:32,870 --> 00:27:35,550
You sneaked in pretending to be a model.

354
00:27:35,550 --> 00:27:39,100
And you accusing me of showing no compassion.

355
00:27:39,100 --> 00:27:43,740
Do you know what will happen if you get caught by a senior manager here?

356
00:27:43,740 --> 00:27:45,700
- I...
- Stay where you are.

357
00:27:50,080 --> 00:27:52,890
Isn't it because I had no other way?

358
00:27:52,890 --> 00:27:57,330
I called you and you wouldn't answer. You never agreed to see me.

359
00:27:57,330 --> 00:28:00,120
This may be a bad idea, but it's all I could do.

360
00:28:00,860 --> 00:28:02,630
Let's cut to the chase.

361
00:28:02,630 --> 00:28:05,340
Tell me. What do you want from me?

362
00:28:07,360 --> 00:28:11,470
We are rushing into business, aren't we now?

363
00:28:11,470 --> 00:28:13,690
No time for some catching up?

364
00:28:16,120 --> 00:28:18,260
Answer me.

365
00:28:22,920 --> 00:28:24,920
All right.

366
00:28:24,920 --> 00:28:27,700
I'm here to talk to you about a cooperation possibility.

367
00:28:27,700 --> 00:28:31,300
Cooperation? With me?

368
00:28:31,300 --> 00:28:34,250
You are not thinking of getting into Cayman in France, are you?

369
00:28:34,250 --> 00:28:36,280
Forget it.

370
00:28:36,280 --> 00:28:38,440
Don't underestimate me.

371
00:28:38,440 --> 00:28:41,130
I guess you don't know.

372
00:28:41,130 --> 00:28:46,500
I'm the girlfriend of the chairman of Haiyao.

373
00:28:48,240 --> 00:28:51,100
So, you came as the boss' woman.

374
00:28:51,100 --> 00:28:54,700
No. I just wanted to tell you

375
00:28:54,700 --> 00:28:59,810
Haiyao is willing to be your foot soldier if that's what you want.

376
00:29:00,660 --> 00:29:02,520
Miss,

377
00:29:03,320 --> 00:29:08,270
do you think I will ever sell my clothes at a grocery store?

378
00:29:08,270 --> 00:29:12,040
Do you not have any idea what Haiyao can or cannot do?

379
00:29:12,040 --> 00:29:14,830
You came here to talk about working with Cayman.

380
00:29:14,830 --> 00:29:17,010
Where did you get that courage?

381
00:29:17,010 --> 00:29:20,400
Director Fang, you have a strong prejudice against Haiyao.

382
00:29:20,400 --> 00:29:23,500
We have boutique stores. We are professional.

383
00:29:23,500 --> 00:29:24,670
Really?

384
00:29:24,670 --> 00:29:28,250
Do you have any decent designers?

385
00:29:29,010 --> 00:29:31,990
Your line of clothes is structurally simplistic

386
00:29:31,990 --> 00:29:33,500
and tedious to look at.

387
00:29:33,500 --> 00:29:37,280
And you strive to be billed as a graceful brand.

388
00:29:37,280 --> 00:29:41,070
You may as well print the words "good taste" on your clothes.

389
00:29:42,500 --> 00:29:47,330
We don't have designers. That's why we would like to codesign with you.

390
00:29:48,750 --> 00:29:51,060
What an idea!

391
00:29:51,060 --> 00:29:54,200
I'll pretend I believe you when you say you came to talk business with me.

392
00:29:54,200 --> 00:29:57,110
But there is no way I will work with Haiyao ever.

393
00:29:57,110 --> 00:30:00,200
Working with Haiyao

394
00:30:00,200 --> 00:30:02,000
would be career suicide.

395
00:30:02,000 --> 00:30:06,230
- How can you think that?
- What should I think?

396
00:30:06,230 --> 00:30:08,810
Think about the cooperation.

397
00:30:10,380 --> 00:30:13,860
Think about all the benefits

398
00:30:13,860 --> 00:30:15,920
of working with us.

399
00:30:15,920 --> 00:30:19,960
You just name your price.

400
00:30:22,730 --> 00:30:26,230
You do have a lot of confidence in yourself, Ms. Bai.

401
00:30:26,230 --> 00:30:28,420
Even if I named my price,

402
00:30:28,420 --> 00:30:30,830
what makes you think you have the authority to negotiate?

403
00:30:32,460 --> 00:30:34,600
I'm making you an offer now.

404
00:30:34,600 --> 00:30:37,860
That's enough authority.

405
00:30:38,820 --> 00:30:41,530
My husband is super good with me.

406
00:30:41,530 --> 00:30:44,330
He does everything I say.

407
00:30:45,230 --> 00:30:47,890
Zhu Haitian is such a loser,

408
00:30:47,890 --> 00:30:50,390
nothing like his father.

409
00:30:54,490 --> 00:30:56,600
Come in. What are you doing?

410
00:30:58,430 --> 00:31:00,150
Shoes.

411
00:31:00,150 --> 00:31:03,060
Ms. Bai, put them on and go.

412
00:31:03,060 --> 00:31:04,900
Director Fang...

413
00:31:04,900 --> 00:31:08,950
You don't want me to call security, do you?

414
00:31:09,620 --> 00:31:11,270
- I...
- Ms. Bai.

415
00:31:11,270 --> 00:31:15,720
Director Fang is very busy. Let's go.

416
00:31:16,690 --> 00:31:18,560
Sneakers?

417
00:31:18,560 --> 00:31:22,410
They don't even go with my look! Fang Xiaoyu!

418
00:31:28,600 --> 00:31:32,200
These are our more in-season type of clothing.

419
00:31:32,200 --> 00:31:36,000
Then we have some pants and skirts. Look at this skirt.

420
00:31:36,000 --> 00:31:39,000
I think it suits you. Do you want to try it?

421
00:31:39,000 --> 00:31:42,100
Okay, please come with me.

422
00:31:51,600 --> 00:31:55,600
You were the one who served that customer?

423
00:31:55,600 --> 00:31:56,900
Yes.

424
00:31:58,100 --> 00:32:03,300
That customer sent a letter to give thanks.

425
00:32:03,300 --> 00:32:06,800
If she is pleased, then that is good.

426
00:32:06,800 --> 00:32:10,800
Have you learned Suzhou Embroidery before?

427
00:32:10,800 --> 00:32:14,400
Yes, you also know?

428
00:32:14,400 --> 00:32:17,800
I know that in China there are many

429
00:32:17,800 --> 00:32:22,200
magnificent embroidery techniques.

430
00:32:22,200 --> 00:32:24,200
I don't believe you.

431
00:32:24,200 --> 00:32:25,800
China...

432
00:32:25,800 --> 00:32:30,200
is improving.

433
00:32:30,200 --> 00:32:33,000
Of course, I am more concerned with the Chinese Market.

434
00:32:33,000 --> 00:32:37,000
At the same time, I hope in our accessories...

435
00:32:37,000 --> 00:32:39,600
there are more Eastern elements.

436
00:32:39,600 --> 00:32:43,900
The Eastern elements today, most of it is a transplant,

437
00:32:43,900 --> 00:32:48,000
it is not the making inside.

438
00:32:48,000 --> 00:32:51,800
There are even many elements that are used wrong.

439
00:32:51,800 --> 00:32:56,600
Not understanding the cultural content.

440
00:32:56,600 --> 00:32:58,600
I agree very much with your insight.

441
00:32:58,600 --> 00:33:03,000
This is also why I have been looking for a new concept.

442
00:33:03,000 --> 00:33:07,200
Do you know Mingyuan Fashion Group?

443
00:33:07,200 --> 00:33:08,400
Yes.

444
00:33:08,400 --> 00:33:10,400
This is a very hard-working

445
00:33:10,400 --> 00:33:13,010
company that really wants to bring

446
00:33:13,010 --> 00:33:16,600
Chinese Culture to the whole world.

447
00:33:16,600 --> 00:33:18,200
Really?

448
00:33:18,200 --> 00:33:20,500
At the same time, their boss

449
00:33:20,500 --> 00:33:23,140
is committed to protecting

450
00:33:23,140 --> 00:33:25,800
craftsman culture.

451
00:33:25,800 --> 00:33:29,200
Suzhou Embroidery is one of them.

452
00:33:29,200 --> 00:33:33,800
I understand. It means that in his hands he has a lot of workshops

453
00:33:33,800 --> 00:33:36,200
that can support their products.

454
00:33:36,200 --> 00:33:37,400
Yes.

455
00:33:37,400 --> 00:33:39,820
His collaboration with them

456
00:33:39,820 --> 00:33:42,000
has preserved the craftsman's living.

457
00:33:42,000 --> 00:33:45,200
At the same time, it has brought

458
00:33:45,200 --> 00:33:50,600
a new design towards accessories.

459
00:33:50,600 --> 00:33:52,200
Just now,

460
00:33:52,200 --> 00:33:57,600
in the back, I saw you send a small cake to your colleague.

461
00:33:58,400 --> 00:34:01,800
Sorry, I shouldn't have...

462
00:34:01,800 --> 00:34:03,600
You misunderstand.

463
00:34:03,600 --> 00:34:05,800
I just feel that dessert

464
00:34:05,800 --> 00:34:09,300
is really beautiful, it is really meaningful.

465
00:34:54,930 --> 00:34:58,250
Okay.

466
00:36:06,700 --> 00:36:08,200
Mo Fei?

467
00:36:08,200 --> 00:36:11,400
Hello, Mengjin where are you?

468
00:36:11,400 --> 00:36:14,000
What's wrong? Are you okay?

469
00:36:14,000 --> 00:36:17,300
I'm having pain in my stomach.

470
00:36:19,800 --> 00:36:23,140
It'll take me two hours to get to your place.

471
00:36:23,140 --> 00:36:25,400
Maybe you should call for an ambulance.

472
00:36:25,400 --> 00:36:29,200
No. Call Fang Xiaoyu. He is right next to us.

473
00:36:29,200 --> 00:36:33,200
That's okay. I'll handle it. Bye.

474
00:36:56,800 --> 00:36:58,200
Hello...

475
00:37:12,800 --> 00:37:15,800
Mo Fei, what's wrong?

476
00:37:15,800 --> 00:37:17,200
Pain in my stomach.

477
00:37:17,200 --> 00:37:18,400
Let me take you to the hospital.

478
00:37:18,400 --> 00:37:20,400
I already called.

479
00:37:20,400 --> 00:37:22,900
We can't wait. I'll make an appointment for you.

480
00:37:24,200 --> 00:37:26,990
That's okay. Let's go.

481
00:37:41,200 --> 00:37:44,000
Hello, this is Paris Medical Center.

482
00:37:44,000 --> 00:37:48,400
Hello, please help me make an appointment for Dr. Michele.

483
00:37:48,400 --> 00:37:52,600
It is really urgent. My name is Fang Xiaoyu.

484
00:37:53,400 --> 00:37:56,000
Mr. Fang, please wait a moment.

485
00:37:57,300 --> 00:38:00,400
After half an hour, Dr. Michele has time.

486
00:38:00,400 --> 00:38:02,200
Okay, thank you.

487
00:38:02,200 --> 00:38:04,200
You're welcome.

488
00:38:21,200 --> 00:38:22,400
- Good evening.
- Good evening.

489
00:38:22,400 --> 00:38:24,600
What is wrong with her?

490
00:38:24,600 --> 00:38:26,000
She has stomach pain.

491
00:38:26,000 --> 00:38:28,000
Can you give her a checkup?

492
00:38:28,000 --> 00:38:32,100
Of course, please wait outside. I'll give her a checkup.

493
00:38:32,830 --> 00:38:36,380
I'll be out there. Call me if you need anything.

494
00:38:42,200 --> 00:38:44,700
Please lie down here.

495
00:38:59,000 --> 00:39:00,600
It's nothing serious.

496
00:39:00,600 --> 00:39:03,800
You have a high white blood cell count. You'll feel better once the inflammation is mitigated.

497
00:39:04,600 --> 00:39:06,400
I was scared.

498
00:39:08,120 --> 00:39:11,320
Can you do me a favor?

499
00:39:12,220 --> 00:39:14,820
What is it? Where does it hurt?

500
00:39:15,800 --> 00:39:18,000
Can you keep this between you and me?

501
00:39:18,000 --> 00:39:22,900
Don't tell anyone I was rushed to the hospital.

502
00:39:27,800 --> 00:39:32,200
By "anyone," you mean Tang Mingxuan, don't you?

503
00:39:34,800 --> 00:39:37,400
I don't want him to worry.

504
00:39:37,400 --> 00:39:40,600
He's been very busy lately. He doesn't have the time.

505
00:39:40,600 --> 00:39:44,400
I don't want to distract him.

506
00:39:44,400 --> 00:39:46,800
- So...
- Okay.

507
00:39:46,800 --> 00:39:50,100
Don't worry. I won't tell him.

508
00:39:50,100 --> 00:39:52,200
But you have to promise me that

509
00:39:52,200 --> 00:39:55,000
you will let me know right away

510
00:39:55,000 --> 00:39:58,000
if something like this happens again. Okay?

511
00:39:59,000 --> 00:40:02,200
You are lucky my family physician was available. You would've been in a lot of pain for a lot longer.

512
00:40:02,200 --> 00:40:04,200
That's enough.

513
00:40:05,100 --> 00:40:07,600
Am I done here?

514
00:40:10,000 --> 00:40:12,800
Almost.

515
00:40:12,800 --> 00:40:16,000
- I'll go get the nurse. Then I'll take you home.
- Hey.

516
00:40:19,030 --> 00:40:23,710
Thank you for today.

517
00:41:08,820 --> 00:41:10,090
Hi!

518
00:41:11,200 --> 00:41:12,600
Mo Fei.

519
00:41:13,800 --> 00:41:16,000
You don't look well. What's wrong?

520
00:41:16,000 --> 00:41:18,800
Really? Is it that bad?

521
00:41:18,800 --> 00:41:21,900
It could be the lighting.

522
00:41:23,200 --> 00:41:25,100
Lighting?

523
00:41:26,600 --> 00:41:29,100
Are you still working?

524
00:41:30,800 --> 00:41:33,600
Yes. There are loads of work to be done.

525
00:41:33,600 --> 00:41:35,000
